44
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:16,360
Where did he go?

45
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,800
I didn't have them tailed

46
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,120
in case he got suspicious.

47
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,420
(Bugao Alley)

48
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,520
